trans-unit.source: Provides a user interface for selecting a file name.
trans-unit.target: 提供用户界面选择的文件名称。

trans-unit.source: FileNameEditor provides a file selection dialog box for file name selection and editing.
trans-unit.target: FileNameEditor 提供用于选择文件名称和编辑的文件选择对话框。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor"></xref> class.
Edits the specified object using the editor style provided by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.GetEditStyle*> method.
trans-unit.target: 编辑指定的对象使用所提供的编辑器样式<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.GetEditStyle*>方法。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.GetEditStyle*>

trans-unit.source: A service provider is provided so that any required editing services can be obtained.
trans-unit.target: 提供的服务提供程序，以便可以获取任何所需的编辑服务。

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref>可以用于获取附加上下文信息。

trans-unit.source: A service provider object through which editing services may be obtained.
trans-unit.target: 通过它可能获得编辑服务服务提供程序对象。

trans-unit.source: An instance of the value being edited.
The new value of the object.
If the value of the object hasn't changed, this should return the same object it was passed.
trans-unit.target: 如果对象的值未发生更改，这应返回同一对象传递给它。

trans-unit.source: Gets the editing style used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.EditValue*> method.
If the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.EditValue%2A> method is not supported, this method will return <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle>.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.EditValue%2A>不支持方法，此方法将返回<xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle>.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.FileNameEditor.EditValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref>可以用于获取附加上下文信息。

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref> values indicating the provided editing style.
trans-unit.target: 之一<xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref>值，该值指示所提供的编辑样式。

trans-unit.source: Initializes the open file dialog when it is created.
trans-unit.target: 创建时初始化打开文件对话框。

trans-unit.source: This method configures the dialog box with a generic file filter and title.
trans-unit.target: 此方法使用泛型文件筛选器和标题配置对话框。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.OpenFileDialog"></xref> to use to select a file name.
